             was indicted for <rs id="t18201206-154-off928" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18201206-154-off928" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201206-154-off928" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
